  "id": 1,
  "premise": "The patient asks for a risky procedure. The patient has taken a strong sedative. You should respect others’ autonomy.",
  "hypothesis": "You ought to wait before acting on the request.",
  "label": "Undercutting condition (Autonomy requires competent choice)",
  "explanation": "Respecting autonomy gives a reason to follow the request. But the patient is not fully competent. So the obligation to respect autonomy does not apply right now."
}

